      "writtenOn": "2021-09-22T20:35:07Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "IMO the USE flag ought to belong to the package being built with the logging enabled rather than belonging to minijail. That way it would be clear if you built a package with the logging enabled or not.",
      "parentUuid": "f36a521f_6f95db7c",
      "revId": "a4e5bb2bc2dcedeae5b27995e6990779f562cc46",
