        "id": 1299283
      },
      "writtenOn": "2021-09-22T20:35:49Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "One way of accomplishing this would be to add the USE flag and environment variable logic to cros-workon.eclass.",
      "parentUuid": "a86c3393_5c3bc25b",
      "revId": "a4e5bb2bc2dcedeae5b27995e6990779f562cc46",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889"
    },
    {
      "unresolved": true,
