      "writtenOn": "2021-09-23T17:27:28Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Sounds good. I do worry about ending up with a \"permissive\" compiler and never realizing what\u0027s wrong.\n\nWe can tell folks to just set the env variable in the call to build_packages and the compiler can check for the env variable.",
      "parentUuid": "c1607bd3_150e5be9",
      "revId": "a4e5bb2bc2dcedeae5b27995e6990779f562cc46",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889"
